      <title>据报道，奥巴马计划很快支持哈里斯担任总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-25/obama-to-reportedly-endorse-harris-for-president-soon-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登在结束连任竞选后首次公开发表讲话。据 NBC 新闻报道，巴拉克·奥巴马计划很快支持卡马拉·哈里斯担任总统。彭博社的 Vonnie Quinn 有详细信息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-25/obama-to-reportedly-endorse-harris-for-president-soon-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:09:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团称重组尽管遭遇挫折但仍在按计划进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/anglo-american-takes-fertilizer-writedown-cuts-diamond-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团表示，尽管煤炭和钻石业务遭遇重大挫折，但仍有望在明年年底前完成彻底重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/anglo-american-takes-fertilizer-writedown-cuts-diamond-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:15:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法航荷航因奥运会影响下调运力预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/air-france-klm-trims-capacity-outlook-amid-bigger-olympics-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于夏季奥运会期间游客避开巴黎，导致客运量下降幅度超预期，法航荷航集团下调了全年运力预期，同时启动了冻结招聘和进一步削减成本的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/air-france-klm-trims-capacity-outlook-amid-bigger-olympics-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合利华季度销售业绩令人失望，转型受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/unilever-turnaround-stumbles-as-quarterly-sales-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于首席执行官海因·舒马赫的扭亏为盈计划未能取得成效，联合利华第二季度销售额增幅低于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/unilever-turnaround-stumbles-as-quarterly-sales-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>炼油业务导致道达尔能源利润下降超预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/totalenergies-profit-drops-more-than-expected-on-gas-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道达尔能源公司公布第二季度利润降幅超预期，因欧洲和中东炼油利润率下降以及天然气价格下跌抵消了油价上涨的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/totalenergies-profit-drops-more-than-expected-on-gas-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:11:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国 Centrica 扩大股票回购以提振投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/uk-s-centrica-extends-share-buybacks-in-boost-to-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Centrica Plc 将延长其向股东返还现金的计划，然后于今年晚些时候对英国 Sizewell C 核电站进行数十亿英镑的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/uk-s-centrica-extends-share-buybacks-in-boost-to-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:10:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stellantis 股价暴跌，盈利下降近一半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/stellantis-earnings-plunged-in-first-half-on-weak-us-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前，Stellantis NV 宣布将恢复销售旧款车型，并考虑降价以应对今年上半年销量的大幅下滑，此后该公司股价一度暴跌 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/stellantis-earnings-plunged-in-first-half-on-weak-us-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:30:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士宝盛利润下滑，Benko 危机后复苏等待新首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/julius-baer-sees-client-inflows-accelerate-amid-benko-clean-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士宝盛集团有限公司 (Julius Baer Group Ltd.) 表示，尽管客户开始返还资金，但今年上半年利润仍然下降，这是去年 Signa 房地产丑闻后复苏不均衡的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/julius-baer-sees-client-inflows-accelerate-amid-benko-clean-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:22:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金属抛售加剧，铜价跌破 9,000 美元大关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/copper-sinks-below-9-000-threshold-as-metals-selloff-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球（尤其是中国）需求前景的悲观情绪加剧，铜价暴跌 - 自 4 月初以来首次跌破每吨 9,000 美元的门槛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/copper-sinks-below-9-000-threshold-as-metals-selloff-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:04:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价下跌，因对中国的担忧抵消了美国库存的下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国经济前景疲软抵消了美国库存下降的影响，油价也随之下跌，大宗商品和股票市场也随之回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 23:19:38 GMT</pubDate>
